lyrics:
[Verse]
I still remember the days we had
Laughing and dreaming, we were best friends
But now you're gone, slipped through my hands
Leaving just memories, my heart won't mend

[Chorus]
Oh, I'm missing you, my dear old friend
Every day feels empty, can't pretend
I wish we could go back, start again
But now I'm left here, lost and heartbroken
